# Phase 2 — Custom Autoregressive Decoder

## Summary

Replaced `model.generate()` with a custom autoregressive decoding loop that instruments every forward pass, producing per-token scientific measurements suitable for mechanistic interpretability research.

```
Prompt → Tokenize → Prefill (KV cache) → Manual Decode Loop → GenerationStep[] → ReasoningTrace → JSON
```

