## Data Structures

### GenerationStep

```python
@dataclass
class GenerationStep:
    step_index: int              # 0-based position
    generated_token: str         # Decoded string
    generated_token_id: int      # Vocabulary index
    timestamp: float             # Seconds since generation start
    top_k_logits: List[TopKEntry]  # Top-5 tokens with logits & probs
    entropy: Optional[float]     # Shannon entropy (nats)
    selected_hidden_states: Dict  # Layer name → vector (empty in JSON)
    finish_reason: Optional[str]  # "eos" | "max_tokens" | None
```

### TopKEntry

```python
@dataclass
class TopKEntry:
    token: str        # Decoded string
    token_id: int     # Vocabulary index
    logit: float      # Raw logit value
    probability: float  # Post-softmax probability
```

